			<p>Hi, I'm Katie! I'm a recent Cognitive Science UC Berkeley grad from the LA South Bay. I've grown up telling stories through my art and illustrations. Throughout my studies, I focused on product design and user experience across interdisciplinary fields, such as education and healthcare.<br> I was recently implementing UX research initiatives to better understand how instructors teach and how students learn at <a href="http://www.cengage.com/us/">Cengage Learning</a>. I was also previously a UX Design Intern at <a href="http://tacchistudios.com/">Tacchi Studios</a> in Tokyo, Japan. I'm currently doing product design consultancy with early stage startups.<br> I love playing video games, spending time outdoors, and doing other paradoxical things. I also pretend that I can sing and play guitar.</br> Let's connect about exciting full-time Product Design opportunities!<br></p>
